In the dim room, a computer screen emits a dazzling blue light, illuminating everything on the table. It was a space full of esports atmosphere, with game posters on the walls, and desktops filled with various game peripherals and keyboard and mouse pads. In the midst of all this, a desk lamp stood quietly.

This desk lamp has a unique shape, like a warship that has traveled from the future. The light body has smooth lines and a sense of technology. The lamp base is made of metal and exudes a cold luster, as if ready to start at any time. Its lampshade is a translucent blue mirror with some mysterious symbols engraved on it, just like ancient runes and the totem of some unknown civilization. Under the reflection of the light, these symbols flash with faint light , adding a hint of mysterious atmosphere to the entire space.

When the desk lamp is turned on, soft light falls on the computer screen, outlining the game screen on the screen more clearly. At this time, the room was echoing with the fierce sound of gunfire, the sound effects of the character's skills during combat, and the nervous and urgent breathing of the player. The light of the desk lamp is like a weapon in the hands of e-sports players, drawing beams of light in the darkness, guiding them to the direction and illuminating the road to victory. It accompanies e-sports enthusiasts who work day and night, becomes their loyal companion on the virtual battlefield, and witnesses the arrival of every moment of glory.
